This repository contains academic coursework and homework assignments for 
Web Development courses. While the code is made public for portfolio purposes,
it is subject to strict academic integrity restrictions.

⚠️  IMPORTANT NOTICE FOR STUDENTS:

If you are currently enrolled in a similar course or working on similar 
assignments:

  ✗ DO NOT copy, use, or submit any part of this code as your own work
  ✗ DO NOT use this code to complete your homework or assignments
  ✗ DO NOT share this code with other students working on similar tasks

Doing so constitutes:
  • Academic dishonesty and plagiarism
  • Violation of your institution's honor code
  • Copyright infringement

Academic plagiarism is detected through:
  • Automated code similarity detection (MOSS, JPlag, Turnitin)
  • Manual instructor review
  • Git commit history and timestamps
  • Cross-institutional plagiarism databases

Consequences may include:
  • Failing grade on the assignment
  • Failing grade in the course
  • Academic probation or suspension
  • Expulsion from your institution
  • Permanent mark on your academic record

